#17503
`8The Keep``~
You have found yourself standing before an immense tower, its sheer
masonry walls spotted with narrow arrow slits.  Breaching the huge wall
before you is a single gate, the gatehouse around which is sealed with a
thick, iron portculis.  To either side of the entryway hangs large banners
heralding the standard of the city.  A single guard, clad in steel finery
stand to each side of the gate, watching closely as a slough of messengers
pour in and out, their arms burdened with important writs and scrolls.  
~
Though night has fallen upon the keep, it is no less busy.  Couriers and
messengers still walk to and fro, and the guards still maintain watch over
all they see.  Torches set in sconces shed their light upon the path below,
and cast eerie, flickering shadows on the standards above.  
~
