`8Royal Court``~
Draped is lavish tapestries laced with gold or silver, a grand room takes
form.  Fine Therian rugs seem to kiss the exotic marble floor ever so
gently.  Lined up near the stonewalls are numerous empty suits of armor that
seem to greet you.  All around, the clatter of people chatting and scarring
about is observed.  
~
