Brilliant beams of light scatter across the stone walls of the barracks,
in a parade of illumination.  Plush canopy beds covered in crushed velvet
bedding are aptly spaced apart.  A large star shaped skylight opens just
enough to allow the suns rays inside to dance about the room.  
~
