#17510
`8The Torture Room``~
The walls about you are of purest black marred only by occasional blood
stains.  Various implements of destruction from simple club to intricate
halberds line the walls, spaced between tools designed more specifically for
extracting pain and suffering.  The floor is crossed with rivets used to
direct the blood away from the giant torture rack in the center to gathering
pools in each corner of the room.  Large handles fill this room with stench
of smoke.  
~
~
