#17513
`8The Royal Treasury``~
The relatively sparse room is dominated by huge chests
which line the far wall. One of the many is open, the
newly minted coins giving off a soft yellow glow when
reflected by the torch-light. A small desk is set in the
center, as if set there for accounting purposes. A few
books are set to one side, alongside an inkwell and a soft
feather quill.
~
